      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "+ Persistencia real:  arquivos JSON  ->  PostgreSQL 16 + SQLModel (ORM)\n+ Migrations versionadas com Alembic  (schema reproduzivel)\n+ Containerizacao:  docker-compose (Postgres)  —  refactor nao tinha Docker\n+ Arquitetura em camadas:  controllers -> services -> entities\n   vs. monolito main.py carregado via importlib\n+ Contratos tipados:  Pydantic schemas (I/O camelCase) + validacao de bbox\n+ Tratamento de erros HTTP (400/404/408/422) + timeout via ThreadPool\n+ Loader idempotente (upsert) + dumps SQL para seed rapido\n+ Testes de integracao (pytest + httpx)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "+ Persistencia real:  arquivos JSON  ->  PostgreSQL 16 + SQLModel (ORM)\n+ Migrations versionadas com Alembic  (schema reproduzivel)\n+ Containerizacao:  docker-compose (Postgres)  —  refactor nao tinha Docker\n+ Arquitetura em camadas:  controllers -> services -> entities\n   vs. monolito main.py carregado via importlib\n+ Contratos tipados:  Pydantic schemas (I/O camelCase) + validacao de bbox\n+ Tratamento de erros HTTP (400/404/408/422) + timeout via ThreadPool\n+ Loader idempotente (upsert) + dumps SQL para seed rapido\n+ Testes de integracao (pytest + httpx)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0O",
      "autoResize": true
    },
